lyrics:
[Verse]
Friday nights, we hit the town
Feeling alive, we're breaking down
Loud music pumping, good vibes all around
We're losing track of time, just floating off the ground

[Chorus]
Un-sober, we're dancing in the haze
No worries left, we're in a daze
We own the night, these memories we'll praise
Un-sober, living life in an electric blaze
